article.description: — Stephane Ingo had 16 points and 10 rebounds to lead Maine to a 59-56 win over New Hampshire on Saturday.
article.headline: Ingo leads Maine over New Hampshire 59-56
article.linkText: Ingo leads Maine over New Hampshire 59-56
article.story: ORONO, Maine -- — Stephane Ingo had 16 points and 10 rebounds to lead Maine to a 59-56 win over New Hampshire on Saturday. Yagodin Mykhailo made two free throws with 13 seconds left for the three-point lead before Marque Maultsby missed a 3-pointer with three seconds left for New Hampshire. Vilgot Larsson had 12 points for Maine (1-3, 1-2 America East Conference). Maultsby had 17 points for the Wildcats (3-3, 2-1). Jayden Martinez added seven rebounds. Blondeau Tchoukuiengo had six rebounds and six assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
